    "en": {
      "title": "Saman Ekanayake appointed as President's Secretary",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ekanayake had previously served as the secretary of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa since Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as Prime Minister in May last year until he resigned.",
        "Prior to that, Ekanayake, who was the secretary to Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe during the period 2015-2019, has now been appointed to the post of President's Secretary.",
        "It is to be noted that Saman Ekanayake is a special grade retired officer in the Sri Lankan Administrative Service."
      ],
